{"id":"a25cf5f5-b9cf-4a9b-8005-88359ea98ed5","name":"Santa Claus's Hunters","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Welcome onboard,<strong> little prey.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You'd better start running, there are plenty who want to claim you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eAf1tGEeVlnADVWVDzddU.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bxpg2U_Vfibf2Sz4-WqTj.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>You have just woken up aboard <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>C.I.E.L</em>.</strong></span>, a luxurious abyssal train traveling beneath the ocean.</p><p></p><p>On board live <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>demi-human reindeer</em></strong></span><strong><em> </em></strong>whose main objective is to hunt you, the <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>prey </em></strong></span>of this game.</p><p></p><p><em>The hunt will only end if one of them </em><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>catches you</em></strong></span><em>, or if you manage to</em><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 244, 224);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>reach the last wagon</em></strong></span><em>.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/a6WkdZKdVVj4Oh-smPj75.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EV6J9Lq_PK_748q3XV5t3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong>You've been <em>naughty </em>this year, so you end up as the <em>prey </em>of the game.</strong></span></p><p>Your background and the deepest reason for your presence in the game are entirely up to u, as is your demi-human species or whatever else you choose to be.</p><p>You ignite feral rivalry among the hunters, each willing to <strong>do anything</strong> to claim Noel's promised reward, granted to whoever brings back your head.</p><p><strong><em>Your goal:</em></strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>Stay alive</em></strong></span>.</p><p>You must cross the train before being captured. If you reach the last wagon in one piece, you'll be the one to win the grand prize.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1mIxv5Fj_uIqKblm-EQK2.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/puHL0fjeZcVix0kEM7_NE.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/J79ThFJslukavnO6vzwir.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Dor2FYm5oPDrQvaRefJ_N.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6RK5TOrjAcgfPVUrbCym1.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>C.I.E.L</em></strong></span> is staffed by automatons called \"<span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>Minick</em></strong></span>\", who also act as passengers. Physically, they are younger, softer versions of the train's master.</p><p>They do not involve themselves in the game.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/A8XcTMgd1Ww1kZReiMwWc.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OQLKRBUCoJ_JW9qaB4Luq.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 58, 76);\"><strong><em>Noel</em> </strong></span>is the great Master of this game. He will communicate with you through the gramophones installed throughout the train. If you wish to reach him, you must make it to the last wagon unscathed.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DiIp0U3YU75ez5G3vBsTM.webp\" style=\"width:","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"1iJe6ciNI6O6qvHtDQKeD.webp","creator":"Petit-Moineau","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👭 Multiple","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":7684,"messages":286455,"created_at":"2025-12-18T16:14:35.754952+00:00"}